                            <comment id="13184808" author="bayard" created="Thu, 12 Jan 2012 08:14:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We should definitely javadoc this. I&apos;m not sure we can do much else. It&apos;d be good to test on the latest JDK to see if it&apos;s been fixed.&lt;/p&gt;

