                            <comment id="13227313" author="bayard" created="Mon, 12 Mar 2012 04:38:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;JDK bug. I&apos;ve made a note in the javadoc of DateFormatUtils (r1299560).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
